[349.50601, "o", "    Iteration 1: Skeptic reviewing...\r\n"]
[369.140596, "o", "    REJECTED: ['MITRE ATT&CK mapping T1567 (Exfiltration Over Web Service) does not match the described behavior. AIM/AOL Instant Messaging uses proprietary protocols (OSCAR protocol), not web services. A more appropriate mapping would be T1048 (Exfiltration Over Alternative Protocol) or T1071 (Application Layer Protocol). The technique ID and technique name are inconsistent with the artifact described.', \"Timeline entries use source type '(mft)' for Firefox browser history entries, which are derived from the Firefox SQLite history database, not the Master File Table. This mislabeling conflates artifact sources and could mislead forensic interpretation.\", \"The narrative references 'subsequent execution of unknown tool HELPER.EXE' as contextual evidence, but no citation for HELPER.EXE is provided anywhere in this finding, making that contextual claim unsupported within the scope of this finding.\"]\r\n    FINAL: rejected after 2 iterations\r\n"]
