[580.63885, "o", "# SIFT Sentinel Investigation Report"]
[580.638895, "o", "\r\n\r\n**Case ID:** m57-jean\r\n**Generated:** 2026-06-11 20:38:33 UTC\r\n**Execution log hash:** `8d4e7be230df0244f0131b1d1287ce7dd94cd13eae47a9152216f7c4a64acfe1`\r\n**Findings accepted:** 7\r\n**Findings unverified:** 2\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Executive Summary"]
[580.639223, "o", "\r\n\r\nThis investigation produced 7 verified finding(s) (1 high, 4 info, 2 low).\r\nMITRE ATT&CK techniques observed: {'technique_id': 'T1036', 'technique_name': 'Masquerading', 'relevance': 'Generic helper-sounding name may be used to disguise malicious binary'}, {'technique_id': 'T1204.002', 'technique_name': 'User Execution: Malicious File', 'relevance': 'Unknown executable with generic name executed multiple times'}, {'technique_id': 'T1547.001', 'technique_name': 'Boot or Logon Autostart Execution: Registry Run Keys', 'relevance': 'No malicious Run key entries found; persistence via this mechanism not confirmed for HELPER.EXE'}.\r\n\r\n## Verified Findings\r\n\r\n### Finding 1: System Identification\r\n\r\n**Severity:** info | **Type:** inferred | **Skeptic iterations:** 2\r\n\r\nThe computer name is JEAN-13FBF038A3 as recorded in the SYSTEM registry hive. The disk contains a single NTFS partition of approximately 10GB. Three non-system user profiles are present: Jean (SID S-1-5-21-484763869-796845957-839522115-1004), Devon (SID S-1-5-21-484763869-796845957-839522115-1007), and Administrator (SID S-1-5-21-484763869-796845957-839522115-500). VMware Tools software is installed and configured to launch at startup via registry Run keys, which is consistent with the system operating as a VMware virtual machine; however, this is an inference from software presence rather than confirmed from BIOS or hardware evidence. The system experienced a boot event on 2008-07-21 at 01:22:01 UTC as evidenced by the NTOSBOOT prefetch entry, followed by an interactive logon event at 01:30:56 UTC as evidenced by the LOGONUI.EXE prefetch entry.\r\n\r\n**Evidence Citations:**\r\n\r\n  [1] `registry_key`: `SYSTEM\\ControlSet001\\Control\\ComputerName\\ComputerName` in `/evidence/disk/nps-2008-jean.E01`\r\n      Excerpt: ComputerName = JEAN-13FBF038A3\r\n  [2] `registry_key`: `SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\ProfileList\\S-1-5-21-484763869-796845957-839522115-1004` in `/evidence/disk/nps-2008-jean.E01`\r\n      Excerpt: ProfileImagePath = %SystemDrive%\\Documents and Settings\\Jean\r\n  [3] `registry_key`: `SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\ProfileList\\S-1-5-21-484763869-796845957-839522115-1007` in `/evidence/disk/nps-2008-jean.E01`\r\n      Excerpt: ProfileImagePath = %SystemDrive%\\Documents and Settings\\Devon\r\n  [4] `registry_key`: `SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion\\ProfileList\\S-1-5-21-484763869-796845957-839522115-500` in `/evidence/disk/nps-2008-jean.E01`\r\n      Excerpt: ProfileImagePath = %SystemDrive%\\Documents and Settings\\Administrator\r\n  [5] `registry_key`: `SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run\\VMware Tools` in `/evidence/disk/nps-2008-jean.E01`\r\n      Excerpt: C:\\Program Files\\VMware\\VMware Tools\\VMwareTray.exe\r\n  [6] `registry_key`: `SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run\\VMware User Process` in `/evidence/disk/nps-2008-jean.E01`\r\n      Excerpt: C:\\Program Files\\VMware\\VMware Tools\\VMwareUser.exe\r\n  [7] `mft_entry`: `11473-128-4` in `/evidence/disk/nps-2008-jean.E01`\r\n      Excerpt: NTOSBOOT-B00DFAAD.pf — run_count: 12, last_run_time: 2008-07-21 01:22:01\r\n  [8] `mft_entry`: `12108-128-4` in `/evidence/disk/nps-2008-jean.E01`\r\n      Excerpt: LOGONUI.EXE-0AF22957.pf — run_count: 53, last_run_time: 2008-07-21 01:30:56\r\n  [9] `byte_offset`: `sector:0000000063` in `/evidence/disk/nps-2008-jean.E01`\r\n      Excerpt: NTFS / exFAT (0x07) partition spanning sectors 63 to 20948759, length 10725732864 bytes (~10GB)\r\n\r\n**Timeline:**\r\n\r\n  - 2008-07-21 01:22:01 (mft): System boot recorded — NTOSBOOT prefetch (MFT entry 11473-128-4, run_count: 12, last_run_time: 2008-07-21 01:22:01) [citation 1]\r\n  - 2008-07-21 01:30:56 (mft): Interactive logon screen displayed — LOGONUI.EXE prefetch (MFT entry 12108-128-4, run_count: 53, last_run_time: 2008-07-21 01:30:56) [citation 1]\r\n\r\n---\r\n"]
